description: TD Global Technology Leaders Index ETF seeks to track, to the extent reasonably possible and before the deduction of fees and expenses, the performance of a global equity index which measures the investment return of global mid- and large-capitalization issuers related to technology. Currently, this ETF seeks to track the Solactive Global Technology Leaders Index (CA NTR) (or any successor thereto), an index calculated by Solactive AG which tracks the performance of securities of global mid- and large-capitalization issuers that are related to technology.
name: TD Global Technology Leaders Index ETF
